  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/720940/extras/5e75acb25af03448d7232e316008c1ec.poster.avif?t=1668535651\" width=508 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/720940/extras/5e75acb25af03448d7232e316008c1ec.webm?t=1668535651\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/720940/extras/5e75acb25af03448d7232e316008c1ec.mp4?t=1668535651\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Horns of Fear is a third-person psychological horror game set in a mysterious mansion. </strong><br><br>You are Jim Sonrimor, a journalist fascinated by the paranormal.<br>Your phone rings one night. The caller invites you to a strange mansion, bordering a forest with a gruesome reputation. Without hesitation, you drive off to visit the place...<br>Embark on this terrifying journey and unravel the mysteries hidden within the mansion.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/720940/extras/17310ca07ac1302a74cf8e3a76a731ec.avif?t=1668535651\" width=638 height=110 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Third-person psychological horror game.<br></li><li>Harrowing exploration and atmosphere.<br></li><li>Items to collect and puzzles to solve.<br></li><li>Made almost entirely by one person.<br></li><li>An original soundtrack by Vinsfeld.<br></li><li>Steam achievements.</li></ul><strong>Warning: </strong><br>This game contains images that some may find disturbing. Have fun!<br><strong>Epilepsy warning:</strong><br>Certain visual effects may be problematic for players with a history of epilepsy.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/720940/extras/5e75acb25af03448d7232e316008c1ec.poster.avif?t=1668535651\" width=508 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/720940/extras/5e75acb25af03448d7232e316008c1ec.webm?t=1668535651\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/720940/extras/5e75acb25af03448d7232e316008c1ec.mp4?t=1668535651\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Horns of Fear is a third-person psychological horror game set in a mysterious mansion. </strong><br><br>You are Jim Sonrimor, a journalist fascinated by the paranormal.<br>Your phone rings one night. The caller invites you to a strange mansion, bordering a forest with a gruesome reputation. Without hesitation, you drive off to visit the place...<br>Embark on this terrifying journey and unravel the mysteries hidden within the mansion.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/720940/extras/17310ca07ac1302a74cf8e3a76a731ec.avif?t=1668535651\" width=638 height=110 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Third-person psychological horror game.<br></li><li>Harrowing exploration and atmosphere.<br></li><li>Items to collect and puzzles to solve.<br></li><li>Made almost entirely by one person.<br></li><li>An original soundtrack by Vinsfeld.<br></li><li>Steam achievements.</li></ul><strong>Warning: </strong><br>This game contains images that some may find disturbing. Have fun!<br><strong>Epilepsy warning:</strong><br>Certain visual effects may be problematic for players with a history of epilepsy.",
